name: Summer of '13 - Pinkalious Dye
description:
Do you roll the Sleeve's up?
Do you keep them Baggy?
Or just cut them off and make a vest? 
The Choice is yours. 
Dyed for your groovy pleasure, each shirt is individual, not one is the same. 
#Chilloutsummer

   Buy the Size up for a Baggy Fit.

   Pink! Aimed this shirt for the ladies but there is nothing wrong with a bit of Pink lads!

We recommend you hand-wash the tee's inside out. If you want to put it in the washing machine you should separate it from other clothes on the first couple of runs. All our tee's have been made so the dye shouldn't run out, but sometimes it may a little. To avoid running of the die, wash on a low temperature. 

All Orders are sent 1st Class.

Sizes:

Small: Chest (inches) 34-36 
Medium: Chest (inches) 38-40 
Large: Chest (inches) 42-44
XL: Chest (inches) 46-48
